font-weight: 400;\">나만의 창작물을 만들어보고 싶으신가요?</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\">예쁜 디자인, 재밌는 게임, 멋진 영상.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">금손들이 만든 작품을 보면서 동경하는 마음과, 나도 해보고 싶은 마음이 들죠.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">하지만, 시작하자니 다들 어떻게 만든 건지 툴도 생경하고 막막해져요.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">그런 고민을 줄여드릴 강의들을 준비해봤어요!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">짜릿한 게임 만들기</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">RPG부터 배틀로얄까지 새로운 세계를 경험하게 해주는 게임 제작</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\">아기자기한 캐쥬얼 게임부터 대서사시가 그려지는 게임까지, 방대한 컨텐츠를 품고있는 게임은 유망한 산업이에요. 게임에 대해서 관심이 있다면 Unity나 Unreal을 배워보세요. 혼자서도 게임을 만들어 볼 수 있답니다.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\"><font color=\"#1dc078\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; cursor: pointer; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/pages/725270d9-8950-4441-ab48-406d971fbc25/retro1.png\" title=\"retro1.png\" width=\"532\" height=\"115\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 3px 15px 0px;\"></span></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-weight: 400;\"