mFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; text-align: center;\">딥러닝이 영상에서 손흥민 선수를 찾아 준다면<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">재미있지 않을까요?</h2><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.1428em; margin-bottom: 0.5714em; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; text-align: center;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Computer Vision분야에서&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">OpenCV</span>와&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">딥러닝</span>을<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">활용하는 방법과 예제를 같이 배웁니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/courses/324508/5600e263-bd23-43ac-b7d9-6487f6c8bcc0/son_recognition.gif\" title=\"son_recognition.gif\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></b></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.3333em; margin-bottom: 0.6666em; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;강의소개</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">인공지능, 머신러닝, 딥러닝을 배우고 강의하면서 이론적인 기초를 다지는 것이 중요한 만큼 실전에서 활용할 능력을 키우는 것도 중요하다고 생각했습니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">그래서 인공지능, 머신러닝, 딥러닝을 사용하는 대표적인 영역인&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Computer Vision분야의 프로젝트</span>를 준비하게 되었습니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">대표적인 이미지, 영상처리 소프트웨어 라이브러리인&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">OpenCV와 딥러닝 모듈인 dnn</span>&nbsp;그리고 다양한 기법과 모듈을 활용하여<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></p><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-size: 17px; border: 1px solid rgb(237, 237, 237); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 40px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: rgb(236, 240, 241); color: rgb(52, 73, 94);\">&nbsp;이미지와 영상처리의 기본을 배우고</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; padding-left: 40px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: rgb(236, 240, 241); color: rgb(52, 73, 94);\">&nbsp;얼굴, 눈 그리고 다양한 물체를 식별하고</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; padding-left: 40px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: rgb(236, 240, 241); color: rgb(52, 73, 94);\">&nbsp;이미지와 영상 속에서 원하는 사람을 학습을 통해 찾아내는</span></p></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">재미있는 과제를 이론과 함께 한단계 씩 배워나갈 수 있도록 강의를 구성했습니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">과정을 마치고나면 다양한 Computer Vision 딥러닝 프로젝트를 꿈꾸게 될 것입니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">저 역시 과정을 만들면서&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">침입탐지, 졸음방지, 숫자나 글씨인식, 감정확인, 나이와 성별인식 등</span>&nbsp;여러 가지 아이디어를 만들고자하는 생각이 들었습니다.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, sys