 system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\">(부제 - 남들 다 해서 나도 안 하면 뒤쳐지는 느낌이 나서 해본 AI)</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 18px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\"></span></span></p><hr><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.3333em; margin-bottom: 0.6666em; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">&nbsp;강의 주제</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.3333em; margin-bottom: 0.6666em; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"></p><pre style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/courses/324850/29e66415-fbf9-4f53-9fd8-536d6d1d7566/son-softbank.png\" style=\"width: 50%;\"></span></pre><pre style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">\"앞으로는 AI의 시대가 올 것이다\"</em></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">― 손정의 소프트뱅크 회장</span></pre><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">굉장히 유명하신 이 분이, 앞으로는 AI의 시대가 올 것이라고 했습니다.</span></div><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">그래서 저도 AI를 배워야 할 것 같아 여기저기 정보를 찾아보고 공부를 시도했으나,</div></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">처음에 머신러닝 개념을 익히기는 쉽지 않았습니다.</div></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\"머신러닝과 딥러닝 차이\" 라고 인터넷에 검색해봤던 기억이 있네요...)</div></span><p></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; padding-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><br><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; box-shadow: rgb(221, 252, 253) 0px -10px inset;\">AI에 처음 입문하는 개발자</span>라면<br>어떻게 하면 좋을까요?</h3><p style=\"text-align: left; box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">아래는 머신러닝 도구인 텐서플로우 홈페이지에 들어가서&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">초보자용</span></span>&nbsp;튜토리얼을 찾아 본 것입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><br></p><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/courses/324850/10370b77-9e1a-4ee0-bedc-795a54fb8b0f/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202020-03-20%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%201.49.52.png\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">초보자용 튜토리얼인데, 처음 보시는 분들은 전혀 이해가 가지 않으실 겁니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">다른 영상과 블로그들을 찾아봐도, 처음 하는 사람을 위해 친절하게 설명해놓은 자료를 찾기 어려워 처음에 고생했던 기억이 납니다.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">입문자분들이 가볍고 쉽게 AI에 대해 한 번 훑고 가는 시간이 되었으면 좋겠습니다.</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; padding-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><hr>&nbsp;강의 특징</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\">초보자가 입문자에게 설명해주는 AI입니다.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">많이 아는 사람이 아닌, 비슷한 눈높이에서 이해할 수 있도록 설명을 드립니다.</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; padding-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><hr>&nbsp;예상되는 질문 QnA</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Q. 강사는 AI 고수인가요?<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></span>A. 아닙니다. AI 초보이고, 이 강의는 초보자가 입문자에게 들려주는 AI 이야기입니다.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarel