le=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">데이터 추출 전문 기능인 파워쿼리</span>가 추가되었습니다.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.1428em; margin-bottom: 0.5714em; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.125; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span>파워쿼리란?</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Helvetica; background-color: rgb(245, 247, 249);\"><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/courses/325241/88d7afb9-5a7d-425f-b58b-10242340e3fb/byj-excel-data-img1.jpg\" title=\"byj-excel-data-img1.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"408\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-a